{UTF-8}
Development Rate=Experienced Staff * Productivity per Person
	~	Task/Month
	~		|

Experienced Staff= INTEG (Hiring Rate,
		5)
	~	Person
	~		|

Hiring Rate=5 / Training Delay
	~	Person/Month
	~		|

Max Prod=10
	~	Task/Person/Month
	~		|

Productivity per Person=Max Prod / (1 + Staff Communication Overhead/100)
	~	Task/Person/Month
	~		|

Staff Communication Overhead=Experienced Staff^1.5
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Tasks Completed= INTEG (Development Rate,
		0)
	~	Task
	~		|

Tasks Remaining= INTEG (-Development Rate,
		500)
	~	Task
	~		|

Training Delay=2
	~	Month
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 24
	~	Month
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Month
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Month [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 0.125
	~	Month [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

